data.description: Fresh neutral paint and new pics!! Come home to this beautiful custom home in the heart of Haughton. Property offers a large lot, 3 car garage, open floor plan and tons of space! 6 bedrooms plus a flex space that could be an office, dining room or sitting area. Beautiful wood and tile flooring throughout main living areas. Granite countertops. Stainless appliances. Beautiful floor to ceiling brick fireplace. Built in coat rack, crown and chair rail details...too many unique features to list. Come see for yourself! Freshly stained stairs and fresh paint! Haughton schools and just minutes to Barksdale AFB.
